title: War of the Roses: The Poem To Win Him Back
description: Courtney wants her ex boyfriend back.  They broke up and she has an idea of how to win him back but doesn't know if he's seeing someone new yet.  So we try War of the Roses on him and then she attempts to win him back with a poem.
